   31 **Data Flows (between Entities, Processes, and Data Stores):**                                                                                                                                          
   33 *   **User Authentication (P1):**                                                                                                                                         
   34     *   E1 -> P1: Registration Data (Email, Username, Password), Login Credentials (Email, Password)                                                                      
   35     *   P1 -> DS1: Store User Credentials                                                                                                                                 
   36     *   DS1 -> P1: Authentication Status, User ID                                                                                                                         
   37     *   P1 -> E1: Authentication Result (Success/Failure), User ID                                                                                                        
   38                                                                                                                                                                           
   39 *   **User Profile Management (P2):**                                                                                                                                     
   40     *   E1 -> P2: Profile Update Request (Username, Profile Picture)                                                                                                      
   41     *   P2 -> DS2: Store User Profile Data (users collection)                                                                                                             
   42     *   DS2 -> P2: Retrieve User Profile Data                                                                                                                             
   43     *   P2 -> E1: Display Profile Data, Profile Update Confirmation                                                                                                       
   44                                                                                                                                                                           
   45 *   **Listing Management (P3):**                                                                                                                                          
   46     *   E1 -> P3: Create Listing Request (Details, Images), View Listings Request, Edit/Delete Listing Request, Mark as Sold Request (Buyer ID)                           
   47     *   P3 -> DS2: Store Listing Data (listings collection), Retrieve Listing Data, Update Listing Status                                                                 
   48     *   DS2 -> P3: Listing Information                                                                                                                                    
   49     *   P3 -> E1: Display Listings, Listing Status Updates                                                                                                                
   50                                                                                                                                                                           
   51 *   **Chat Management (P4):**                                                                                                                                             
   52     *   E1 -> P4: Initiate Chat Request (Listing ID), Send Message (Text, Listing Context)                                                                                
   53     *   P4 -> DS2: Store Chat Metadata (chats collection), Store Messages (messages subcollection), Update Unread Count                                                   
   54     *   DS2 -> P4: Retrieve Chat History, Unread Counts, Other User Profile (from users collection)                                                                       
   55     *   P4 -> E1: Display Chat History, New Messages, Unread Indicators                                                                                                   
   56                                                                                                                                                                           
   57 *   **Image Handling (P5):**                                                                                                                                              
   58     *   E1 -> P5: Image File (for Listing/Profile)                                                                                                                        
   59     *   P5 -> DS3: Store Image File                                                                                                                                       
   60     *   DS3 -> P5: Image URL                                                                                                                                              
   61     *   P5 -> P2/P3: Image URL (for Profile/Listing)    
   